PixelZoo:
A client-server architecture for cellular automata simulations.

Dependencies
============

Core client: C code in src/, compiles into lib/
-----------

libxml2 (MIT license, included by default with the iPhone SDK)


Xcode client: Objective-C and Xcode IDE files in xcode/pixelzoo/
------------

Requires Xcode and iOS development framework.


Android client: Java/C code and Eclipse IDE files in android/
--------------

Requires Eclipse and Android SDK/NDK.


Server: Perl code in Zoo/
------

Perl Catalyst, and a few other modules.
Do 'cd Zoo; perl Makefile.PL; make' to install other dependencies from CPAN.

